{
  "_comment": "Per-slug viewmodel overrides. Omitted slugs get the default viewmodel (production, page template, pages.{slug} scope, lang+spiral-fab features). Only non-default pages need entries here. 'title' is used by build-archives.js to display the dev section — it is not consumed by the God Script assembler.",

